  <brief_title>The Effect of the Oligofructose Supplementation on Body Weight in Overweight and Obese Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of the Oligofructose Supplementation on Body Weight in Overweight and Obese Children: a Randomized, Double Blind, Placebo-controlled Trial</official_title>
